headline: Eagle Foods Marks Tenth Anniversary as Sales of Portfolio of Popular Brands Continue to Climb
summary: CLEVELAND, October 07, 2025--Eagle Foods—the consumer packaged goods company behind such brands as Hamburger Helper, Suddenly! (pasta sides), Eagle Brand® Sweetened Condensed Milk, Popcorn Indiana and Cretors—is marking a major milestone as it celebrates its tenth anniversary.
